The theorem statement is:
`ρ.IsAutomorphicOfLevel p hV S ↔ (ρ.map (algebraMap F E)).IsAutomorphicOfLevel p hV (HeightOneSpectrum.preimageComapFinset (𝓞 F) F E (𝓞 E) S)`

