The problem asks to complete a Lean 4 proof for a theorem named `cyclic_base_change`. This theorem relates the automorphicity of a Galois representation `ρ` of a number field `F` to the automorphicity of its base change `ρ | Gal(E/F)` to an extension `E` of `F`, under certain conditions.

